==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Halves
<hw>Halves</hw> <pr>(h⟦aum⟧vz)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>, <def><pos>pl.</pos>
of <er>Half</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>By halves</b></col>, <cd>by one half at once; halfway;
fragmentarily; partially; incompletely.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I can not believe by <qex>halves</qex>; either I have faith, or I
have it not.</q> <rj><qau>J. H. Newman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>To go halves</b></col>. <cd>See under
<er>Go</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Halwe</ent>⟦br⟧
